         <abstract>
            <p>A general formula is developed which gives the "best" approximation for any linear functional on the Hardy space H&lt;sup&gt;2&lt;/sup&gt;. Some "best" approximations are given for interpolation, differentiation, and integration and are compared to polynomial approximations.</p>
          </abstract>
